    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h2 id="化学热力学"><a href="#化学热力学" class="headerlink" title="化学热力学"></a>化学热力学</h2><h3 id="1-你需要知道的基础知识"><a href="#1-你需要知道的基础知识" class="headerlink" title="1.你需要知道的基础知识"></a>1.你需要知道的基础知识</h3><h4 id="理想气体状态方程"><a href="#理想气体状态方程" class="headerlink" title="理想气体状态方程"></a>理想气体状态方程</h4><script type="math/tex; mode=display">pV=nRT</script><p><strong><em>p</em></strong>为压强，单位是Pa、<strong><em>V</em></strong>为体积，单位是dm<sup>3</sup>、<strong><em>n</em></strong>是物质的量，单位是mol、<strong><em>T</em></strong>是温度，单位是K、<strong><em>R</em></strong>是摩尔气体常数。</p><a id="more"></a><p>与n相关还有三个公式：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">n=\frac{m}{M}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">n=\frac{N}{Na}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">c=\frac{n}{V}</script><p>与V相关还有一个公式：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\rho=\frac{m}{V}</script><h4 id="内能"><a href="#内能" class="headerlink" title="内能"></a>内能</h4><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\Delta U=Q+W</script><p><strong><em>U</em></strong>为内能、<strong><em>Q</em></strong>为热量、<strong><em>W</em></strong>为功</p><h3 id="2-焓"><a href="#2-焓" class="headerlink" title="2.焓"></a>2.焓</h3><p>定义焓（<strong><em>H</em></strong>）：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">H=U+pV</script><p>在等压条件下（此时<strong><em>Q</em></strong>为<strong>等压热效应<em>Q<sub>p</sub></em></strong>）当体系做的功仅为体积功时：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">W=W_e=-p\Delta V</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\because \Delta U=Q_P+W</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\therefore \Delta U=Q_p-p\Delta V</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\therefore U_2-U_1=Q_p-p(V_2-V_1)</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\therefore (U_2+pV_2)-(U_1+pV_1)=Q_p</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\therefore H_2-H_1=Q_p</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\therefore \Delta H=Q_p</script><p>此时焓变即反应热</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\Delta _fH^\Theta_m</script><h2 id="未完待续"><a href="#未完待续" class="headerlink" title="未完待续"></a>未完待续</h2>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
